<BR>&nbsp;
<BLOCKQUOTE><B>"... 10% of the work force, were fired</B>

<P><B>for sending e-mail that violated standards</B>

<P><B>at the NY Times Co.'s business office</B>

<P><B>[in Norfolk, Virginia]."</B>

<P><B>employees had sent or forwarded</B>

<P><B>"potentially offensive e-mails"</B></BLOCKQUOTE>


